ārabbha bhikkhū āmantesi – ‘‘bhikkhavo’’ti. ‘‘Bhadante’’ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. Bhagavā etadavoca –

‘‘Puna  caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na sikkhākāmo hoti, sikkhāsamādānassasikkhākāmassa 
Note { id=9, line='85', referenceLine='106', original='sikkhākāmassa (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na sikkhākāmo hoti, sikkhāsamādānassa '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='sikkhāsamādānassa'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='sikkhākāmassa'}}
na vaṇṇavādī. Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na sikkhākāmo hoti sikkhāsamādānassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati.

‘‘Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ na paṭisanthārakopaṭisandhārako 
Note { id=10, line='94', referenceLine='114', original='paṭisandhārako (ka.)', type='auto', previous='Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ na paṭisanthārako '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='paṭisanthārako'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='paṭisandhārako'}}
hoti, paṭisanthārakassa na vaṇṇavādī. Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ na paṭisanthārako hoti paṭisanthārakassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati.

‘‘Evarūpassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya – ‘aho vata  maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃgarukareyyuṃ 
Note { id=11, line='103', referenceLine='115', original='garukareyyuṃ (sī. syā.)', type='auto', previous=' maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='kareyyuṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā.', text='garukareyyuṃ'}}
 māneyyuṃ pūjeyyu’nti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī na ceva sakkaronti na garuṃ karontigarukaronti 
Note { id=12, line='112', referenceLine='115', original='garukaronti (sī. syā.)', type='auto', previous=' māneyyuṃ pūjeyyu’nti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī na ceva sakkaronti na garuṃ karonti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='karonti'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā.', text='garukaronti'}}
na mānenti na pūjenti. Taṃ kissa hetu? Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū sabrahmacārī te pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne samanupassanti.

‘‘Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkosakaparibhāsako ariyūpavādī sabrahmacārīnaṃ ṭhānametaṃ avakāso 
Note { id=13, line='121', referenceLine='131', original='aṭṭhānametaṃ anavakāso (sī. syā. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkosakaparibhāsako ariyūpavādī sabrahmacārīnaṃ ṭhānametaṃ avakāso '
