yaṃ so dasannaṃ byasanānaṃ aññataraṃ byasanaṃ nigaccheyya 
Note { id=14, line='130', referenceLine='131', original='na nigaccheyya (sī. syā. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' yaṃ so dasannaṃ byasanānaṃ aññataraṃ byasanaṃ nigaccheyya '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='nigaccheyya'}
